OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1774707082
OL,3,CAlderney pupils go on strike claiming
OL,4,Cschool is letting them down
OL,6,FPupils studying for their GCSEs at
OL,7,FAlderney's secondary school walked out
OL,8,Fto protest at the poor standard of
OL,9,Feducation they say they've received.
OL,11,FThe eight students in the year group
OL,12,Fat St Anne's School held a quiet
OL,13,Fprotest in the memorial garden,
OL,14,Ffollowed by a meeting with Alderney
OL,15,FStates members yesterday (March 26th)
OL,16,Frather than attending lessons.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
