FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1774707082
OL,3,CAlderney pupils go on strike claiming
OL,4,Cschool is letting them down
OL,6,FA parent of one of the students, who
OL,7,Fwished to remain anonymous, told ITV
OL,8,FNews that maths is the worst subject
OL,9,Ffor the youngsters, as they've had
OL,10,Feight teachers in two years.
OL,12,FThey added that there's been disputes
OL,13,Fbetween the school and teachers, which
OL,14,Fhave lead to them leaving.
OL,16,FAs a result of the disruption, they
OL,17,Ffeel their child is "not confident at
OL,18,Fall" about their upcoming GCSEs and
OL,19,Fthere are "big gaps" in their learning.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1774707082
OL,3,CAlderney pupils go on strike claiming
OL,4,Cschool is letting them down
OL,6,FThe parent went on to say they feel
OL,7,Ftheir child will be two grades below
OL,8,Fwhat they are capable of because of
OL,9,Fthe disruption and stated "it's too
OL,10,Flate for this Year 11 cohort now".
OL,12,FLast year's GCSE results showed an
OL,13,Fimprovement on the previous year, with
OL,14,F60% of students achieving Grade 4 and
OL,15,Fabove in all subjects. But this was
OL,16,Flower than Guernsey's States
OL,17,Fmaintained schools (63.2%) and the UK
OL,18,Faverage ( 67.1%)
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1774707082
OL,3,CAlderney pupils go on strike claiming
OL,4,Cschool is letting them down
OL,6,FNick Hynes, Director of Education,
OL,7,Fsaid: "In recent weeks we have been
OL,8,Fworking closely with St Anne's in
OL,9,FAlderney to provide additional support
OL,10,Ffor the GCSE cohort currently
OL,11,Fpreparing to take their exams."
OL,13,F"Students and their parents and carers
OL,14,Fhave raised concerns around disruption
OL,15,Fto their learning because of staff
OL,16,Fturnover."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1774707082
OL,3,CAlderney pupils go on strike claiming
OL,4,Cschool is letting them down
OL,6,F"I fully recognise that many students
OL,7,Fmay be feeling frustrated and that
OL,8,Fthere has been disruption to their
OL,9,Flearning, and we understand that this
OL,10,Fis an important and sometimes
OL,11,Fstressful time for them."
OL,13,FHe added: "However, I know the school
OL,14,Fhas been addressing these issues with
OL,15,Findividual mentoring sessions and
OL,16,Fputting on additional revision
OL,17,Fsessions on a range of subjects both
OL,18,Fduring the holidays and after school."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1774707082
OL,3,CAlderney pupils go on strike claiming
OL,4,Cschool is letting them down
OL,6,F"We are also discussing the
OL,7,Fpossibility of subject specialists
OL,8,Ffrom Guernsey going to Alderney next
OL,9,Fterm for further revision sessions.
OL,10,FAll of this work is being done with
OL,11,Fthe aim of helping every student
OL,12,Fsucceed."
OL,14,F"St Anne's, the Education Office, and
OL,15,Fmore recently, the Governing Board
OL,16,Fhave all been making sustained efforts
OL,17,Fto address the root of these
OL,18,Fchallenges as well, particularly
OL,19,Faround staffing."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1774707082
OL,3,CAlderney pupils go on strike claiming
OL,4,Cschool is letting them down
OL,6,F"Recruiting skilled teachers to work
OL,7,Fin St Anne's continues to be
OL,8,Fdifficult, especially in attracting
OL,9,Fstaff to work on the island, but this
OL,10,Fremains a priority.
OL,12,F"I have been informed that because of
OL,13,Ftheir frustrations, Year 11 students
OL,14,Fin St Anne's did not attend school
OL,15,F(26th). Clearly, attending school and
OL,16,Fengaging with the support available is
OL,17,Fthe best way to ensure students are
OL,18,Ffully prepared for exams."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1774707082
OL,3,CAlderney pupils go on strike claiming
OL,4,Cschool is letting them down
OL,6,F"As part of my regular interaction and
OL,7,Fvisits to the school I will be in St
OL,8,FAnne's early in the Easter term, and I
OL,9,Fwill make sure that I am available,
OL,10,Falongside other officers, to speak to
OL,11,Fparents, carers and students so they
OL,12,Fcan ask any questions they may have."
OL,14,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,15,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,16,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,17,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,18,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,19,Fbelow...
